        { kind:"hotel",   name:"Spillstattstrasse 27", note:"Early dinner in village — try Onkel Tom's Hütte (wood-fired pizza, casual) or a cozy stube. Early night for tomorrow's full day at First + Lauterbrunnen.", photoUrl:PHOTOS.grinhotel }
