  "The sole surviving city gate of medieval Delft — built around 1400 in Brick Gothic style with twin Gothic towers and a former drawbridge. Upper levels converted to residential spaces. Perfect final shot of Delft before dinner.": "中世纪代尔夫特唯一幸存的城门 — 建于 1400 年左右，采用砖砌哥特式风格，拥有双哥特式塔楼和一座前吊桥。上层改建为住宅空间。晚餐前代尔夫特的完美最后一击。",
  "Dinner in Delft": "代尔夫特晚餐",
